column26:
Steps to reproduce:

# Navigate to the marketing page
# Click on “Add” 
# Enter  257 characters in "Tracking code" field 

Expected result:

"Tracking code” field should not accept 257 characters and should give an error message.

Actual result:

"Tracking code" field is accepting 257 characters and also showing a message “ Success: You have modified marketing tracking\!” but it is not reflecting the same in the marketing tracking list with 257 characters. It is reflecting only 64 characters.
